  "page": "Did you know/10",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that when <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a> was betrothed to <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey Baratheon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a> proposed betrothing <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Myrcella_Baratheon\" title=\"Myrcella Baratheon\">Myrcella Baratheon</a> once she would came of age?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/10&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_47\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 47\">Chapter 47</a>, Eddard XIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404083123\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 103/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8542/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 426/2097152 byt